 adjusts her shoulder slightly—the strap sliding a fraction of an inch. The side light now touches the edge of the red ribbon, making it stand out against her blonde hair, and a faint rustle of fabric mingles with the distant chirp of a bird. The background remains a soft blur, keeping focus on her and her uniform’s tactile details. *"],"shape":2},{"id":90,"type":"CLIPTextEncode","pos":[-870.6756337000479,727.4284369033043],"size":[325.02242346346,88],"flags":{"collapsed":false},"order":22,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"CLIP","localized_name":"clip","name":"clip","type":"CLIP","link":165},{"localized_name":"文本","name":"text","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"text"},"link":247}],"outputs":[{"label":"条件","localized_name":"条件","name":"CONDITIONING","type":"CONDITIONING","links":[166]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.26","Node name for S&R":"CLIPTextEncode","ue_properties":{"version":"7.5.2","widget_ue_connectable":{"text":true},"input_ue_unconnectable":{}},"widget_ue_connectable":{"text":true}},"widgets_values":[""],"shape":1},{"id":7,"type":"CLIPTextEncode","pos":[-772.1214498113138,861.5008888530795],"size":[340.7936166581319,184.8563702452111],"flags":{"collapsed":true},"order":15,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"CLIP","localized_name":"clip","name":"clip","type":"CLIP","link":75},{"localized_name":"文本","name":"text","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"text"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"label":"条件","localized_name":"条件","name":"CONDITIONING","type":"CONDITIONING","slot_index":0,"links":[98]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.46","Node name for S&R":"CLIPTextEncode","ue_properties":{"version":"7.5.2","widget_ue_connectable":{"text":true},"input_ue_unconnectable":{}},"widget_ue_connectable":{"text":true}},"widgets_values":["色调艳丽，过曝，静态，细节模糊不清，字幕，风格，作品，画作，画面，静止，整体发灰，最差质量，低质量，JPEG压缩残留，丑陋的，残缺的，多余的手指，画得不好的手部，画得不好的脸部，畸形的，毁容的，形态畸形的肢体，手指融合，静止不动的画面，杂乱的背景，三条腿，背景人很多，倒着走, censored, mosaic censoring, bar censor, pixelated, glowing, bloom, blurry, day, out of f